<item>
            <title>[LU-7241] sanity test_60a: there are no more free slots in catalog</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7241</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/9e244b8a-680e-11e5-8b6d-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/9e244b8a-680e-11e5-8b6d-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_60a failed with the following error in the MDS console log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;04:00:31:Lustre: 20633:0:(llog_test.c:1496:llog_test_10()) 10e: write 65536 more log records
04:00:31:Lustre: 20633:0:(llog_cat.c:93:llog_cat_new_log()) MGS: there are no more free slots in catalog
04:00:31:LustreError: 20633:0:(llog_test.c:1501:llog_test_10()) 10e: write 65536 records failed at #61705: -28
04:00:31:Lustre: 20633:0:(llog_test.c:1565:llog_test_10()) 10f: put newly-created catalog
04:00:31:LustreError: 20633:0:(obd_config.c:575:class_setup()) setup llt_name failed (-28)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This has been failing intermittently since 2015-09-09 17:13:22:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/45204452-573e-11e5-b624-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/45204452-573e-11e5-b624-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is likely the result of newly-landed llog tests around that time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 60a&lt;/p&gt;</description>
